92
00:05:53,940 --> 00:05:56,270
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">That's right... Did I even tell you my name?</font>

93
00:05:58,270 --> 00:06:00,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">So it was you, Lola?!</font>

94
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,030
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm so glad I got to see you again!</font>

95
00:06:02,030 --> 00:06:02,730
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Lola, you mean...</font>

96
00:06:02,730 --> 00:06:04,540
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Whoa, hey! Wait a second!</font>

97
00:06:04,540 --> 00:06:06,280
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Could she really be that boar-zombie?!</font>

