<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Oh, thanks!</font>

122
00:07:08,730 --> 00:07:10,210
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">How is he?</font>

123
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:14,390
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">This is the first time Zoro's been this badly injured...</font>

124
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:17,020
