125
00:07:17,020 --> 00:07:20,680
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I just know it... Something must have happened to him...</font>

126
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:22,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">While we were unconscious...</font>

127
00:07:24,690 --> 00:07:29,530
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Indeed. It's hard to believe that that man would just leave like that.</font>

128
00:07:29,530 --> 00:07:32,330
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's also weird that Luffy is so energetic all of a sudden, isn't it?</font>

129
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:35,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I have no idea how that happened either!</font>

130
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:39,370
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What happened, huh?</font>

131
00:07:39,790 --> 00:07:41,060
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Actually, I saw it all!</font>

132
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:43,510
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I saw all of it, too!</font>

133
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:44,910
