140
00:08:00,610 --> 00:08:03,040
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What happened afterwards?</font>

141
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:06,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">After I fainted, I mean.</font>

142
00:08:09,930 --> 00:08:13,100
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Well, that Warlord had another crazy power, you see!</font>

143
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:16,500
