<font face="Impress BT" size="55">He didn't risk his life so that we'd praise him about it.</font>

157
00:09:06,490 --> 00:09:07,800
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">And besides...</font>

158
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:12,800
