166
00:09:42,230 --> 00:09:44,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Hey, you two.</font>

167
00:09:44,530 --> 00:09:48,330
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You said you knew something earlier, right?
What did you see?</font>

